<td colspan="2" style="padding: 0px; padding-top: 2px; text-align:center; font-size:100%;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Christian_Bale_-_002.jpg" class="image" title="Christian Bale - 002.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/Christian_Bale_-_002.jpg/180px-Christian_Bale_-_002.jpg" width="180" height="271" border="0" /></a><br />
