<th>Born</th>
<td>Christian Charles Philip Bale<br />
30 January 1974 <span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1974-01-30</span>)</span> <span class="noprint">(age&#160;35)</span><br />
<a href="/wiki/Haverfordwest" title="Haverfordwest">Haverfordwest</a>, <a href="/wiki/Pembrokeshire" title="Pembrokeshire">Pembrokeshire</a>, <a href="/wiki/Wales" title="Wales">Wales</a><sup id="cite_ref-Wills_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Wills-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>, <a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom" title="United Kingdom">United Kingdom</a></td>
